Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:05.08,Staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,片源：chiwa\N壓製：xelnaga
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.51,0:00:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在我的書裡讀到了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我根本比不上姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.25,0:00:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心﹐我一定會保護妳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.12,0:00:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.36,0:00:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起﹐對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瀧浦老師的稿子\N今天好像終於可以寫好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能跟妳一起去\N真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.14,0:00:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正在第一線寫作的人\N比較重要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是這個意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.25,0:00:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有記者會和簽書會而已對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.45,0:00:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該會有導遊\N在那邊的機場等妳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.26,0:00:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳一定要回來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.33,0:00:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.31,0:01:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（歡迎堇川嚕嚕嚕老師）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是堇川老師嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.13,0:01:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是導遊﹐蜜雪兒．張
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今年24歲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.20,0:01:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喜歡的書是“哈利波特”系列…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.04,0:01:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫奈奈奈﹐堇川奈奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是嚕嚕嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.31,0:01:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚕嚕嚕？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奈奈奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.81,0:01:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先帶妳到下榻的飯店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪姬﹐瑪姬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.24,0:02:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳跑到哪裡去了？真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在老師面前這樣說很失禮耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是司機﹐叫瑪姬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪姬沉默寡言﹐沒什麼表情\N個子長得很高
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喜歡的作家是海明威
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.82,0:02:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來沒什麼女人味\N不過是個好女孩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姊姊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對﹐我們是姊妹﹐感情很好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請上車
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我雖然喜歡海明威
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也很喜歡堇川老師的書
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為要改拍成電影\N現在在日本也很轟動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.69,0:03:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為那本書是在四年前出版的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從那之後半本都沒寫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對﹐我在日本已經是個\N被遺忘的作家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香港島
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那座島就是香港島
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旁邊是九龍半島
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在開會之前\N請好好休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.56,0:03:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳的房間是\N最頂樓的景觀套房
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耍小聰明的日本母狗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和爛文一起下地獄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知廉恥的電影公司\N也給我好好反省
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是犯罪聲明\N但是沒有署名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好遲到了﹐因此逃過一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是誰幹的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是反日的瘋狂激進派
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳知道是誰幹的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然要取消囉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.39,0:04:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是\N堇川老師的安全第一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣夾著尾巴回去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不就等於是輸給那個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被一個笨蛋瞧不起\N我豈能悶不吭聲？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意思要我加派警力\N保護妳的任性是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.74,0:04:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任性？我哪裡任性了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我的尊嚴問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙想用暴力\N抹殺我的書
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且﹐我根本不期待警方的保護
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我出道十年來\N一直被這些笨蛋追著跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是﹐我從來沒有屈服過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之﹐明天我要簽名簽到底
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有種就來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會用油性簽字筆在犯人臉上\N畫一個禁止播映的符號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這才叫作家﹐真有男子氣概
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點都不像女生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天的警衛任務\N能不能也讓我們參加？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是導遊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我不能放著堇川老師不管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算拼上性命也要保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說的是瑪姬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的﹐可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的﹐了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切會照預定計劃進行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也會派人保護妳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫堇川老師找新的飯店…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.89,0:06:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請小心走喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們家在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偵探？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的﹐這才是我們的正業
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.95,0:06:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果要找人、書、貓\N請務必找我們商量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀﹐完蛋了完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是“書崩”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個月已經是第五次了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們家的老么艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最討厭書了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要叫那麼大聲﹐妳這個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是奈奈奈﹐堇川奈奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇怪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.84,0:07:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要讓一個\N素昧平生的人住到家裡來？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳這是什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們都是老師的忠實書迷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更何況作者\N就等於是我們的親人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒看過她的書
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作家老師願意住到家裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對愛書狂而言\N可是光榮之至的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是什麼愛書狂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像打擾到你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師﹐請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在舉行三姊妹會議
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贊成的人舉手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反對的人舉手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好﹐決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不公平﹐太專橫了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是民主的解決方法喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.96,0:08:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下能不能請妳\N在這本書上簽名？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要﹐我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（嚴禁作家及攜帶書籍入內）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到底在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姊姊﹐姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個老師不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一帶晚上很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說對不起就沒事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回家了啦﹐快來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想起了以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寫這本書的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很喜歡看書\N一直埋在書堆裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我姊姊們一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人說很喜歡我寫的書
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是個怪胎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是有一天﹐那個人不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不告而別﹐突然就走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也沒來得及問那個人\N對這本書的感想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得不知道那個人的感想\N就無法繼續寫下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳很喜歡他嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是女生啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過﹐該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與其說是喜不喜歡\N應該說她是個很重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很重要的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯﹐她真的是個愛書人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得她可能窩在\N某家書店裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣也很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.61,0:12:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是妳很重要的人不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.98,0:12:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然這樣\N有一天總會見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經四年音訊全無了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不相干啦\N世界就是這樣形成的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳還真是人小鬼大啊﹐小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳才是呢\N不要像小孩一樣給別人添麻煩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回家吧﹐姊姊他們很擔心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蜜雪兒說的夢話很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳也那麼認為嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-目前沒有異常狀況\N-也沒有發現可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才好像在網路上做出了警告\N說要襲擊老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新作品請多加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了簽名以外的東西\N全都不能帶進來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是我的書
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯﹐這是我的書
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准動！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則我會引爆炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯人出現了\N身上帶著爆炸物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身高170﹐削瘦型的男子\N身分不明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把武器扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裡面的球碰到兩側\N就會爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是個作家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種三流的日本作家…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在好幾個月前\N就帶那本書來找過我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼這傢伙的爛故事\N居然還拍成電影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的小說卻沒有人看？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起﹐我太緊張了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要隨便亂動\N小心我轟掉這裡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要亂來\N只不過是本小說而已不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不過是本小說？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是賭上了我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我生於這個國家\N長於這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犧牲一切寫出了這本小說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你們卻只會捧\N這種外來的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯﹐我是外來者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我的小說\N並不是什麼外來者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.34,0:15:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論是誰都能來翻我的書看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少廢話！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你也是作家\N就用你的作品殺了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕對不會死於這種炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡﹐妳死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躺在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師呢？老師平安無事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躺在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們會操紙術？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳認識這個人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有看過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出了什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,順便看看他寫什麼好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等妳看完了再讓我看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要向你們道謝\N畢竟你們救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要謝的話﹐就給我們錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是蜜姊跑到哪裡去了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.71,0:17:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼好道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來﹐這個給妳\N也有蜜雪兒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我會把它當作傳家之寶的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太誇張了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳也有一本啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿去賣會有多少錢呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳跑去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙已經走了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.09,0:18:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,筆跡…有兩種
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那本小說是合寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作者還有另外一個人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我弟弟承蒙妳照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個都瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼不把這種熱情\N投注在作品裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是因為熱情太豐富了\N才導致我們這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:19:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳應該明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是說﹐妳已經江郎才盡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.80,0:19:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別拿我跟你們相提並論
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們只是躲在\N寫小說遊戲裡的人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行﹐進不去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪姬﹐到前面去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看前面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還活著嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳來這裡幹什麼？小不點\N太危險了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳對救命恩人\N居然是這樣的說話態度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過﹐這下我們扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次要給我更厚的書喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我不太會防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少囉嗦﹐妳這小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,墜機？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心﹐有姊姊他們在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姊姊﹐好重…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.53,0:21:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來讓它變輕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,997號班機\N現在依然下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-媽媽﹐那是什麼？\N-大家要相信我們公司的駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個是光拿著\N就能得到好運的磁壺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.32,0:22:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪姬﹐妳沒去過神保町吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.56,0:22:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.73,0:22:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說那裡是\N世界上書最多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.37,0:22:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下去逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.81,0:22:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.24,0:22:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳就隨便想個藉口吧\N這個妳很拿手不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.41,0:22:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹出這麼扯的騷動\N誰想得出藉口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.98,0:22:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退稿啦﹐退稿\N太沒有真實感了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.58,0:22:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真過份﹐不知感恩的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.05,0:22:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是說了這樣剛好扯平嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.17,0:23:11.97,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,珍藏的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.04,0:23:17.88,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總是凋零散落
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:21.78,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唯有和你的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.85,0:23:27.12,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,深烙在我心深處
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.86,0:23:33.82,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逐漸轉涼的海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.90,0:23:39.70,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩人嬉戲的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:44.14,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與你曬得黝黑的皮膚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.21,0:23:49.27,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,融化在西沉的夕陽裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.65,0:23:55.05,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但願牽著的手永不分離
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.12,0:24:02.96,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣長大成人該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.03,0:24:10.02,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在陽光下追逐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.10,0:24:14.20,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尋找你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.27,0:24:20.94,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感受到戀情結束的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.01,0:24:24.50,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相互依偎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.58,0:24:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#01 漫天紙舞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.24,0:24:37.64,preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇﹐好大…好棒的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.71,0:24:39.68,preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.74,0:24:41.00,preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實也還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.08,0:24:44.31,preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然一個人住這麼大的房子　太臭屁了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.38,0:24:46.44,preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-房租要多少錢呢？　-臭屁？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.52,0:24:47.41,preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一百萬
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.82,0:24:49.61,preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.69,0:24:51.85,preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？不要亂摸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.32,0:24:53.31,preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-不要睡在那裡　-好難喝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.39,0:24:53.98,preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-我去洗個澡　-好難喝的牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.06,0:24:55.72,preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要埋到書堆裡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.96,0:25:00.43,preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蜜姊﹐瑪姊又哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.50,0:25:03.47,preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是不是把別人的家當成自己家了？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.70,0:25:08.10,preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.31,0:25:10.27,preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.81,0:25:16.07,preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪姬哭了﹐怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.98,0:25:19.64,preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-當作沒聽到吧　-書書書？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.72,0:25:21.01,preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰來拿本書給她看吧
